    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem. It's in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. It drives perfectly and looks even better in person. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the massive price tag, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
