    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the original factory scent lingers. Every switch, button, and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive folder of meticulous dealership service records and a spotless undercarriage. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen a drop of rain. For the buyer who demands perfection and a 'no-stories' history, this example is unparalleled.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
