      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting flawless coachwork and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously serviced and rigorously inspected, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For the discerning individual who demands nothing less than perfection, this motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class.",
