    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and has been kept in pristine condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for your next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great new home!",
