    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This collector-grade example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the rod bearing service is documented, the VANOS system has been fully overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The chassis remains exceptionally tight with no bushing play, and the original suspension geometry is perfectly preserved. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a flawless interior, this is a turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
